    "Recent work has also unveiled jailbreak attacks within the context of multilingual scenarios (Deng et al., 2023), and non-natural languages such as ciphers (Yuan et al., 2023), in-context learning (Qiang et al., 2023), highlighting the risk for all open-source LLMs with modified decoding strategies (Huang et al., 2023)."
  ]
